		<bioghist encodinganalog="MARC 545">
			<head altrender="biography" id="a2">BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE </head>
			<p>Inga Lohne Brauner was a reconstruction aide and nurse during World War I. She was
				the second wife of Olaf Brauner, a Cornell University professor and artist.</p>
		</bioghist>
